  <title>Which target types are supported?</title>

  <p>The following types of targets are supported:</p>

  <list>
    <item><p>CMP DigitalTarget</p></item>
    <item><p>ColourChecker 24</p></item>
    <item><p>ColourChecker DC</p></item>
    <item><p>ColourChecker SG</p></item>
    <item><p>i1 RGB Scan 14</p></item>
    <item><p>LaserSoft DC Pro</p></item>
    <item><p>QPcard 201</p></item>
    <item><p>IT8.7/2</p></item>
  </list>

  <note style="tip">
    <p>You can purchase targets from well-known vendors like KODAK, X-Rite and LaserSoft in various online shops.</p>
    <p>Alternatively you can buy targets from <link href="http://www.targets.coloraid.de/">Wolf Faust</link> at a very fair price.</p>
  </note>

